Code preview of the table PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYS.SYSREFERENCES R JOIN SYS.SYSOBJECTS O ON (O.ID = R.CONSTID AND O.TYPE = 'F')
WHERE R.FKEYID = OBJECT_ID('PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT') AND O.NAME = 'FK_PARTICIP_SCREENING_SCREENIN')
ALTER TABLE PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT
DROP CONSTRAINT FK_PARTICIP_SCREENING_SCREENIN
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSOBJECTS
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT')
AND TYPE = 'U')
DROP TABLE PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT */
/*==============================================================*/
CREATE TABLE PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT (
PARTICIPANT_ID BIGINT NOT NULL,
SCREENING_ID BIGINT NULL,
NHS_NUMBER BIGINT NULL,
REASON_FOR_REMOVAL VARCHAR NULL,
REASON_FOR_REMOVAL_DT DATE NULL,
BUSINESS_RULE_VERSION VARCHAR NULL,
EXCEPTION_FLAG CHAR NULL,
RECORD_INSERT_DATETIME TIMESTAMP NULL,
RECORD_UPDATE_DATETIME TIMESTAMP NULL,
CONSTRAINT PK_PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT PRIMARY KEY (PARTICIPANT_ID)
)
go

ALTER TABLE PARTICIPANT_MANAGEMENT
ADD CONSTRAINT FK_PARTICIP_SCREENING_SCREENIN FOREIGN KEY (SCREENING_ID)
REFERENCES SCREENING_LKP (SCREENING_ID)
go
